legs.start_address: Kültür, Atatürk Blv. No:16, 49300 Muş Merkez/Muş, Turkey

steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto Erzurum Cd./Muş Bitlis Şosesi/D300/D955
Continue to follow Erzurum Cd./D300/D955
Kulp Yolu turns slightly right and becomes Kulp Köprüsü

Slight right onto Diyarbakır Bitlis Yolu/D360/E99
Continue to follow D360/E99

Continue onto Şanlıurfa Diyarbakır Yolu/D360/E99
Continue to follow Şanlıurfa Diyarbakır Yolu/E99

Keep left at the fork and merge onto E90
Partial toll road

Take the exit toward Tarsus-Ankara Otoyolu/O-21/E90
Toll road

Take the exit toward O-21A/E90
Toll road
Keep left to continue on Adana Konya Yolu
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on Yeni Çevre Yolu

Turn right onto Üçgöz Cd./D350
Continue to follow D350
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Ereğli Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Dr. Aziz Tarhan Cd.

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Atatürk Blv.
Destination will be on the right
